snippet.title: Bang Showbiz
snippet.description:
BANG Showbiz brings you the latest video celebrity stories, these are produced to the clients requirements which could
include your branding, presenter and language. We provide Voice Over in English, Spanish, French, Italian, German, Portuguese,
Russian, Chinese and Japanese. (please find examples in the 'languages playlist').

BANG Showbiz has a great reputation in the celebrity world and receives accreditation to the top premieres, award ceremonies and fashion shows. 

So be sure to Subscribe for the latest celebrity and showbiz news content!
